{"words":[{"word":"into","count":4},{"word":"ano","count":4},{"word":"septimont's","count":4},{"word":"unwritten","count":4},{"word":"yes","count":3},{"word":"augusta","count":3},{"word":"dark","count":3},{"word":"new","count":3},{"word":"iuno","count":3},{"word":"fear","count":2},{"word":"grandmother","count":2},{"word":"lillibet","count":2},{"word":"glimpse","count":2},{"word":"auguries","count":2},{"word":"fate","count":2},{"word":"end","count":2},{"word":"tide's","count":2},{"word":"cut","count":2},{"word":"miasma","count":2},{"word":"tide","count":2},{"word":"someone","count":2},{"word":"name","count":2},{"word":"flames","count":2},{"word":"finds","count":1},{"word":"gifted","count":1},{"word":"successor","count":1},{"word":"future","count":1},{"word":"light","count":1},{"word":"apprentices","count":1},{"word":"carving","count":1},{"word":"insights","count":1},{"word":"stone","count":1},{"word":"passing","count":1},{"word":"words","count":1},{"word":"along","count":1},{"word":"flowed","count":1},{"word":"thread","count":1},{"word":"guided","count":1},{"word":"reverent","count":1},{"word":"seekers","count":1},{"word":"surge","count":1},{"word":"overturned","count":1},{"word":"soul","count":1},{"word":"spared","count":1},{"word":"arrived","count":1},{"word":"afar","count":1},{"word":"join","count":1},{"word":"forces","count":1},{"word":"corrosaurus","count":1},{"word":"bait","count":1},{"word":"male","count":1},{"word":"female","count":1},{"word":"reveal","count":1},{"word":"truth","count":1},{"word":"false","count":1},{"word":"sovereign's","count":1},{"word":"blood","count":1},{"word":"ruler","count":1},{"word":"crowned","count":1},{"word":"prophesied","count":1},{"word":"averted","count":1},{"word":"thanks","count":1},{"word":"longer","count":1},{"word":"grips","count":1},{"word":"retreats","count":1},{"word":"forgotten","count":1},{"word":"night","count":1},{"word":"countless","count":1},{"word":"souls","count":1},{"word":"drink","count":1},{"word":"pure","count":1},{"word":"waters","count":1},{"word":"hero","count":1},{"word":"heroes","count":1},{"word":"lead","count":1},{"word":"septimont","count":1},{"word":"age","count":1},{"word":"thus","count":1},{"word":"present","count":1},{"word":"aligns","count":1},{"word":"prophecy","count":1},{"word":"foresaw","count":1},{"word":"leave","count":1},{"word":"baffled","count":1},{"word":"suggesting","count":1},{"word":"recounting","count":1},{"word":"missed","count":1},{"word":"named","count":1},{"word":"find","count":1},{"word":"familiar","count":1},{"word":"hmm","count":1},{"word":"speak","count":1},{"word":"impossible","count":1},{"word":"priestess","count":1},{"word":"certainty","count":1},{"word":"none","count":1},{"word":"among","count":1},{"word":"bear","count":1},{"word":"must","count":1},{"word":"remind","count":1},{"word":"rarely","count":1},{"word":"take","count":1},{"word":"part","count":1},{"word":"hunts","count":1},{"word":"place","count":1},{"word":"sacred","count":1},{"word":"tetragon","count":1},{"word":"temple","count":1},{"word":"hunt","count":1},{"word":"sovereign","count":1},{"word":"involved","count":1},{"word":"many","count":1},{"word":"perhaps","count":1},{"word":"mistaken","count":1},{"word":"confused","count":1},{"word":"else","count":1},{"word":"shot","count":1},{"word":"moon","count":1},{"word":"arrow","count":1},{"word":"mean","count":1},{"word":"dispelled","count":1},{"word":"cliffside","count":1},{"word":"struck","count":1},{"word":"sword","count":1},{"word":"remember","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"...Yes, I fear that until Grandmother Lillibet finds a gifted successor, we shall not glimpse further into <ano= Septimont's Auguries>Septimont's future</ano>.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"By the light and fate above us, we are but apprentices carving insights into stone, passing their words along.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"Once, fate flowed like a thread. It guided reverent seekers to glimpse Septimont's end...","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"Under the Tide's surge, all was overturned. No soul was spared.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"Until the Unwritten One arrived from afar to join forces with Augusta.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"With the Corrosaurus as bait, {Male=he;Female=she} cut through the Dark Tide's miasma to reveal the truth.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"With the False Sovereign's blood, a new ruler was crowned. The prophesied end was averted, thanks to Augusta and the Unwritten One.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"From now on, fear no longer grips me. The Dark Tide retreats into the forgotten night, and countless souls drink from pure waters again. The new Hero of Heroes, Augusta, shall lead Septimont into a new age.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"Thus, the present now aligns with the prophecy Grandmother Lillibet once foresaw in Septimont's Auguries.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"Who is... Iuno?","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"Unwritten One, you leave me baffled.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"Are you suggesting that my recounting missed... someone named Iuno? I don't find the name... familiar.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"Hmm. I should know this... Iuno, you speak of, yes?","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"Impossible. As a Priestess myself, I can tell you with certainty that none among us bear that name.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"And, I must remind you, we rarely take part in hunts. Our place is with the <ano=Sacred Flames>flames</ano> in Tetragon Temple.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"The hunt for the Sovereign involved many. Perhaps you are mistaken and confused her for someone else?","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"Who shot the Moon Arrow...? What do you mean? You were the one who dispelled the miasma.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"Yes. On the cliffside, you struck with your sword to cut through the Dark Tide. Don't you remember, Unwritten One?","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001}]}